    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2-generation Carrera 4S represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance, featuring the iconic wide-body silhouette and the M96/03 3.6L flat-six engine. The powertrain is in superlative condition, featuring a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a proactive cooling system refresh with an upgraded water pump and low-temp thermostat. Power is delivered through a crisp six-speed manual transaxle and a sophisticated viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system that ensures optimal traction without sacrificing steering feel. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec, with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers providing a compliant yet communicative ride. Meticulously maintained with a flawless DME overrev report, the exterior retains its original depth and luster, while the cabin shows no signs of bolster wear or UV degradation on the switchgear. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example for the discerning purist.",
